---
title: Sichuan Beef Noodle Soup with Green Beans & Baby Leaves
description: This Sichuan-flavoured soup will warm you up from the inside out! Beef mince, mixed veggies and golden egg noodles all come
together in a warm and comforting broth that’s packed full of flavour. Perfect for chilly days, this will fulfill any comfort-food needs.
